data.name: TEST WORKOUT
data.brief: This is a test workout to test different combinations of exercise and get ready timespans.

data.name: WORKOUT FOR TEST
data.brief: This is a test workout to test different combinations of exercise and get ready timespans.

data.name: 7M TABATA
data.brief: A tabata inspired workout that includes a warmup and cooldown. Although short, this workout is intense. Make sure you are physically fit before attempting.

data.name: BURN 100
data.brief: A high intensity workout that will help you burn 100 calories in just 15 minutes.

data.name: EASY HIIT
data.brief: A longer HIIT workout with more rest between intervals for those that are still getting used to going all out. Easier to perform but just as sweat inducing.

data.name: FAT BLASTING HIIT
data.brief: Turn the fat burn up a level with this 10 minute high intensity workout that will really get you moving.

data.name: FULL BODY HIIT
data.brief: Nothing beats a full body HIIT workout. 4 circuits of upper and lower body movements with ample rest in between. Perfect for those new to HIIT.

data.name: GET PUMPED
data.brief: A longer routine that will hit your body hard. Help builds both strength and endurance.

data.name: HARD CORE
data.brief: Get rock hard abs with this intense high intensity workout.

data.name: HIIT 10
data.brief: A 10 minute high intensity workout that will make you sweat. Highly efficient and effective for losing weight.

data.name: HIIT 15
data.brief: Let's see what we can accomplish with this heart pumping, calorie burning, 15-minutes HIIT workout.

data.name: HIIT 20
data.brief: Our most intense workout. A tough workout that will get your blood pumping. Not for beginners!

data.name: HIIT LOWER BODY
data.brief: This is a quick burn legs workout. It will help melt more fat away in less time.

data.name: HIIT & ABS
data.brief: This high intensity standing workout will work your abs hard. An ab workout with no seated movements? Yes indeed!

data.name: TABATA BODY
data.brief: The most efficient way to workout. Burn 15 calories a minute and work the whole body in just 4 minutes!

data.name: TABATA BURPEES
data.brief: This is a 4 minute Tabata workout where all you do is burpees! Excruciatingly fun... for some people!

data.name: TOTAL HIIT
data.brief: Maximize your fat burn with this 10-minute ultra high intensity interval workout. You really got to bring it for this one. Not for the faint of heart!
